## ‚è≥ Operating System Development Timeline  

| Era        | Key Developments |
|------------|----------------|
| **1940s**  | No OS, manual programming |
| **1950s**  | Batch processing OS appears |
| **1960s**  | Time-sharing & **MULTICS, UNIX** |
| **1970s**  | UNIX grows, CLI-based OS |
| **1980s**  | GUI OS (MacOS, Windows 1.0) |
| **1990s**  | Linux, Windows 95, Internet OS |
| **2000s**  | Mobile OS (Android, iOS), Virtualization |
| **2010s**  | Cloud computing, Docker, Kubernetes |
| **2020s**  | AI-driven OS, Edge Computing |

---

